<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 14:04:04 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>英国财长称俄罗斯对莫斯科的攻击只是“烟幕弹”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/russian-accounts-of-moscow-attack-a-smokescreen-says-uk-finance-minister/articleshow/108749754.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108749754.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;英国财政大臣杰里米·亨特表示，英国对俄罗斯有关最近莫斯科音乐厅袭击事件的声明“几乎没有信心”，并声称俄罗斯正在寻求为其在乌克兰的行动辩护。莫斯科克洛库斯市政厅发生的袭击造成 133 人死亡，伊斯兰国组织声称对此负责。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 10:36:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/russian-accounts-of-moscow-attack-a-smokescreen-says-uk-finance-minister/articleshow/108749754.cms</guid></item><item><title>教宗跳过棕枝主日讲道但继续服务</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/pope-skips-palm-sunday-homily-but-continues-service/articleshow/108749756.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108749756.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;教皇方济各因健康问题放弃了通常的讲道朗诵，这让圣彼得广场圣枝主日弥撒的与会者感到惊讶。这位87岁的教皇一直在与支气管炎和流感作斗争，他让一名助手宣读了他准备好的演讲稿。这种偏离传统的做法引起了人们的注意，因为教皇很少在如此重要的活动中完全跳过讲道。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 10:40:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/pope-skips-palm-sunday-homily-but-continues-service/articleshow/108749756.cms</guid></item><item><title>前斯里兰卡人普雷兹因评论 2019 年复活节爆炸事件而面临调查</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/ex-sri-lankan-president-faces-inquiry-after-claiming-to-know-mastermind-behind-2019-easter-bombings/articleshow/108749318.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108749318.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 10:12:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/ex-sri-lankan-president-faces-inquiry-after-claiming-to-know-mastermind-behind-2019-easter-bombings/articleshow/108749318.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列对黎巴嫩东部巴勒贝克的袭击造成四人受伤</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/four-wounded-in-israeli-strikes-on-east-lebanons-baalbek/articleshow/108749694.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108749694.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据法新社记者报道，以色列在黎巴嫩巴勒贝克附近的空袭造成四人受伤，击中了一栋两层建筑。自加沙冲突开始以来，以色列和哈马斯盟友真主党之间的跨境交火不断升级。随着以色列多次空袭真主党据点巴勒贝克地区，人们对全面战争的担忧加剧。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 10:33:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/four-wounded-in-israeli-strikes-on-east-lebanons-baalbek/articleshow/108749694.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯向乌克兰发射57枚巡航导弹侵犯波兰领空</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-launches-57-cruise-missiles-at-ukraine-violates-polands-airspace/articleshow/108749032.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108749032.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯对乌克兰发动第三次导弹袭击，第二次瞄准基辅。波兰报告俄罗斯巡航导弹短暂侵犯其领空。当火箭从北方逼近时，基辅处于高度戒备状态。没有人员伤亡报告。波兰要求莫斯科做出解释，强调结束冲突。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 10:13:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-launches-57-cruise-missiles-at-ukraine-violates-polands-airspace/articleshow/108749032.cms</guid></item><item><title>船倾覆后，三名罗兴亚难民被发现死在海中</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/three-rohingya-refugees-found-dead-in-sea-after-boat-capsizes/articleshow/108748530.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108748530.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;亚齐附近的搜寻工作结束，发现三具罗辛亚难民尸体。 75名获救人员被转移。班达亚齐搜救机构负责人、难民署工作人员协助确认死者身份。 70 名失踪或死亡的罗兴亚难民引发担忧。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 09:55:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/three-rohingya-refugees-found-dead-in-sea-after-boat-capsizes/articleshow/108748530.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦：遏制非法烟草贸易是国际货币基金组织提供资金的关键条件</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-curbing-illicit-tobacco-trade-a-key-condition-for-funding-by-imf/articleshow/108748346.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108748346.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 09:54:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-curbing-illicit-tobacco-trade-a-key-condition-for-funding-by-imf/articleshow/108748346.cms</guid></item><item><title>比拉瓦尔·布托在胡里节向巴基斯坦的印度教社区致以祝福</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/bilawal-bhutto-wishes-hindu-community-in-pakistan-on-holi/articleshow/108748163.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108748163.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴基斯坦前外交部长比拉瓦尔·布托在洒红节向该国的印度教社区致以祝福，声称这一节日提醒人们超越宗教或文化差异的共同人性。巴基斯坦人民党（PPP）主席在一份声明中强调了促进包容性和尊重国内多元文化传统的重要性。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 09:05:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/bilawal-bhutto-wishes-hindu-community-in-pakistan-on-holi/articleshow/108748163.cms</guid></item><item><title>波兰武装部队称俄罗斯在袭击乌克兰时侵犯了波兰领空</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-violates-polands-air-space-in-attack-on-ukraine-polands-armed-forces-say/articleshow/108748367.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108748367.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;波兰武装部队报告称，俄罗斯周日早些时候向乌克兰西部的目标发射了一枚巡航导弹，侵犯了其领空。武装部队在社交媒体平台X上表示：“3月24日凌晨4点23分，俄罗斯联邦远程航空夜间发射的一枚巡航导弹侵犯了波兰领空。”</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 09:16:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-violates-polands-air-space-in-attack-on-ukraine-polands-armed-forces-say/articleshow/108748367.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯对基辅发动空袭，乌克兰防空回应</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-conducts-air-strike-on-kyiv-ukraines-air-defence-responds/articleshow/108743711.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108743711.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;乌克兰官员报告称，俄罗斯对基辅发动空袭，但遭到乌克兰防空系统的反击。市长克里琴科证实首都发生爆炸，军队正在参与防御。目击者听到爆炸声并看到空中武器被拦截。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 04:26:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-conducts-air-strike-on-kyiv-ukraines-air-defence-responds/articleshow/108743711.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯谴责俄罗斯恐怖袭击事件引发网上批评</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hamas-condemns-terror-attack-in-russia-sparking-online-criticism/articleshow/108747079.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108747079.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;哈马斯领导人向俄罗斯最近发生的恐怖袭击事件的受害者表示哀悼，莫斯科附近有 133 人丧生。伊斯兰国-呼罗珊声称对此负责。尽管与以色列发生冲突，哈马斯仍然支持俄罗斯。哈马斯在激进组织关系复杂的情况下谴责暴力行为，网上批评者质疑其诚意。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 08:11:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hamas-condemns-terror-attack-in-russia-sparking-online-criticism/articleshow/108747079.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列官员透露美国与哈马斯交换人质囚犯的提议</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-official-reveals-us-proposal-for-hostage-prisoner-exchange-with-hamas/articleshow/108747296.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108747296.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国在以巴谈判中提出了一项囚犯交换计划，涉及哈马斯释放的被监禁的巴勒斯坦人和人质。中央情报局局长威廉·伯恩斯（William Burns）促进了在汇率问题上存在分歧的谈判。以色列同意美国的过渡提议，等待哈马斯的回应。停战谈判旨在停止加沙攻势并从最近发生的事件中解救人质。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 08:21:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-official-reveals-us-proposal-for-hostage-prisoner-exchange-with-hamas/articleshow/108747296.cms</guid></item><item><title>致命的食肉细菌感染在日本迅速蔓延</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/deadly-flesh-eating-bacterial-infection-spreading-rapidly-in-japan/articleshow/108746395.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108746395.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一种致命的食肉细菌感染——链球菌中毒性休克综合症（STSS），死亡率高达30%，正在日本迅速蔓延。美国国家传染病研究所披露，2023 年确诊病例为 941 例，2024 年病例数将继续激增。医学专家建议保持卫生习惯以防止其传播。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 08:08:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/deadly-flesh-eating-bacterial-infection-spreading-rapidly-in-japan/articleshow/108746395.cms</guid></item><item><title>塞尔维亚人对特朗普家族就北约爆炸地点达成的协议感到愤怒</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/serbians-angry-at-trump-family-deal-for-site-of-nato-bombing/articleshow/108745957.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108745957.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 07:57:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/serbians-angry-at-trump-family-deal-for-site-of-nato-bombing/articleshow/108745957.cms</guid></item><item><title>200多名尼日利亚学生在卡杜纳北部被绑架后获释</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/more-than-200-nigerian-students-released-after-abduction-in-northern-kaduna/articleshow/108746198.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108746198.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;卡杜纳州长办公室周日证实，距离 69 万美元赎金截止日期仅几天，在尼日利亚北部被绑架的 200 多名学生和教职员工已获释，安然无恙。这起事件于 3 月 7 日在卡杜纳州库里加发生，这是该国自 2021 年以来首次发生大规模绑架事件，当时一所高中有 150 多名学生被绑架。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 07:40:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/more-than-200-nigerian-students-released-after-abduction-in-northern-kaduna/articleshow/108746198.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴西一名女孩在风暴造成至少 12 人死亡 16 小时后从废墟中撤离</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/a-girl-in-brazil-recused-from-rubble-after-16-hours-as-storm-kills-at-least-12/articleshow/108745025.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108745025.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴西东南部因暴风雨导致房屋倒塌，一名小女孩被困在废墟下16个多小时，最终被成功救出。可悲的是，女孩的父亲发现她身旁已无生命迹象，于是用自己的身体保护了她。风暴造成了毁灭性的损失，导致当局向里约热内卢州的山区派遣救援队。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 06:43:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/a-girl-in-brazil-recused-from-rubble-after-16-hours-as-storm-kills-at-least-12/articleshow/108745025.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦外长表示“认真”考虑恢复与印度的贸易关系</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/seriously-considering-trade-ties-restoration-with-india-says-pakistan-foreign-minister/articleshow/108744325.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108744325.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴基斯坦外交部长穆罕默德·伊沙克·达尔表示愿意认真考虑恢复与印度的贸易关系，该关系自 2019 年 8 月以来一直处于搁置状态。在因废除第 370 条而紧张之后，这一立场标志着巴基斯坦对印度的外交态度可能发生转变。坚称印度必须扭转其在克什米尔的行动，以此作为对话的先决条件，但印度拒绝了这一要求</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 05:31:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/seriously-considering-trade-ties-restoration-with-india-says-pakistan-foreign-minister/articleshow/108744325.cms</guid></item><item><title>德国面临人力短缺，大学生成为电车运营商</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/university-students-become-tram-operators-as-germany-faces-manpower-shortage/articleshow/108743993.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108743993.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 05:24:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/university-students-become-tram-operators-as-germany-faces-manpower-shortage/articleshow/108743993.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国油轮在也门海域遭胡塞武装袭击</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/chinese-owned-oil-tanker-attacked-off-yemen-by-houthi-rebels/articleshow/108743593.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108743593.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国军方表示，周六，一艘中国油轮在也门附近遭到胡塞武装发射的弹道导弹袭击，胡塞武装加强了对红海航运的打击。中央司令部表示，胡塞叛军在黄浦号附近的红海发射了四枚反舰弹道导弹，随后第五枚击中了该船。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 04:05:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/chinese-owned-oil-tanker-attacked-off-yemen-by-houthi-rebels/articleshow/108743593.cms</guid></item><item><title>西班牙：法官下令全国封锁 Telegram</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/spain-judge-orders-telegram-to-be-blocked-nationwide/articleshow/108743236.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108743236.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 03:45:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/spain-judge-orders-telegram-to-be-blocked-nationwide/articleshow/108743236.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>